{"tid":538862,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"走同留既決擇","createTime":"2018-01-24T04:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T05:34:13.000Z","uid":106019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf77c63eebc121ff3edaf1208a2df8c03c8f99f","tid":538862,"uid":106019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"小弟就27，澳洲野雞marketing grad。兩年前開始做野，入左一行幾偏既行業。兩年內轉左兩次工，而家做第三份。但做落有d唔對路，我部門得我一個，因為係啱啱開無耐，而且前人留低好多屎係到，做左3個月想走。<br />\n<br />\n我同老細講，佢加人工留我，呢個價都係我出去諗住搵工既價，但而家做既野我覺得唔太啱自己，我內向，但係呢個post應該係要比較主動。<br />\n<br />\n想問下走定留好，如果走想去做建築行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622b62b06a88212021cc97805a539d670f6f3a78","tid":538862,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"咁咪主動啲囉<br />\n價位又啱自己<br />\n一世內向咩"},{"pid":"1467df28e6672f3d726c53bfed67908f9ac7db3c","tid":538862,"uid":35666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622b62b06a88212021cc97805a539d670f6f3a78","tid":538862,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"咁咪主動啲囉<br />\n價位又啱自己<br />\n一世內向咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52022a07e962b1822825ed4df78313f703aac64","tid":538862,"uid":106019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622b62b06a88212021cc97805a539d670f6f3a78","tid":538862,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"咁咪主動啲囉<br />\n價位又啱自己<br />\n一世內向咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"問題係呢個位我未做過，一入黎又無人帶，好多野都唔知應該點，好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3832d89e66cdf6f57d838cda36e337b56110d42f","tid":538862,"uid":6594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"唔好做囉, 你上黎問都係想人地推你一把俾D決心你姐"},{"pid":"c1f67cdad0125d9a4d56814c1eb7d164c1767e72","t